text:
Excellent service by smiling employees and beautifully presented food (nevertheless, breakfasts could be improved);
Large and beautiful rooms with the most advanced electronic equipment;
Nice bathrooms in the open air;
In and out, fine pieces of local art show the owners' constant concern about aesthetics;
Lounging in the sun in a comfortable wooden hammock near the pool is a dream
In the morning, walking along the close quiet road leading to a small traditional village not yet destroyed by tourism and modernism is a priceless pleasure.
